<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl">$ go <span class="nb">test</span> -bench<span class="o">=</span>Pool -benchmem
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">goos: linux
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">goarch: amd64
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">pkg: github.com/maolonglong/bytebufferpool
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">cpu: Intel<span class="o">(</span>R<span class="o">)</span> Core<span class="o">(</span>TM<span class="o">)</span> i7-7500U CPU @ 2.70GHz
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">BenchmarkByteBufferPoolBuf-4    <span class="m">20764896</span>                52.71 ns/op            <span class="m">0</span> B/op          <span class="m">0</span> allocs/op
